ard ABUJA - PRESIDENT Muhammadu Buhari has written to the Senate, requesting for the screening and subsequent confirmation of Professor Jumai Audias the Chairman of the Nigerian Law Reform Commission. May 12, 2020 In "News" PRESIDENT Muhammadu Buhari has written to the Senate, requesting for the screening and subsequent confirmation of Professor Jumai Audi as the Chairman of the Nigerian Law Reform Commission. May 12, 2020 In "News" President Muhammadu Buhari has written the Senate to confirm former Inspector-General of Police, Musliu Smith, as the chairman of Police Service Commission, PSC. May 25, 2018 In "News"